---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import BookingForm from '~/components/BookingForm.astro'
import AiAssessmentWidget from '~/components/AiAssessmentWidget.astro'
import avatarImage from '~/content/avatar.jpg'

const appsScriptUrl = 'https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbzpTiA0UIpMDHcMy3188VvDxhyJ_Xc0gbHlMmbLGR7LvdwDMY-viTkHi6ZWorub1MV-KA/exec'
---

<Layout title="AI Competence Development" description="Practical AI upskilling for professionals and teams. Identify your highest-yield AI use cases, get hands-on experience, and walk away with a concrete plan for integrating AI into your daily workflow. 9,900 SEK per session.">
  <article class="max-w-full py-8">
    <header class="mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-xl font-medium text-foreground mb-2">
        AI Competence Development (online)
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 mb-4 text-base text-foreground/90 font-medium">
        Practical upskilling that takes you from surface-level AI usage to real workflow integration — with hands-on experience and a concrete plan to keep building on.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
        <Image
          src={avatarImage}
          alt="Daniel Grahn"
          class="rounded-full border border-foreground/10 size-20 aspect-square"
          width={160}
          height={160}
        />
      </div>
    </header>

    <AiAssessmentWidget appsScriptUrl={appsScriptUrl} />

    <!-- The gap -->
    <div class="py-4 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground/50 font-medium mb-3">AI Competence Development</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
        Knowing where AI fits is the first step. The real value comes from building the competence to use it yourself — in your workflows, with your tools, on your data. This session gives you both the roadmap and the practical skills to get started.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground/50 font-medium mb-6">How it works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-foreground/30 text-sm font-medium shrink-0">01</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground/90">Pre-interview questionnaire</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground/60">You fill out a pre-interview questionnaire about your workflow, tools, processes, and data. I use this to build a session tailored to your actual work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-foreground/30 text-sm font-medium shrink-0">02</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground/90">Online session</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground/60">Working through your workflow in depth — mapping where AI can make the biggest difference, with recommendations tailored to your context. We also address your top use case hands-on so you leave with practical experience, not just a list of ideas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-foreground/30 text-sm font-medium shrink-0">03</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground/90">Follow-up report</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground/60">A written playbook covering everything from the session: AI opportunities mapped to your workflow, recommended tools, and concrete next steps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What you'll walk away with -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground/50 font-medium mb-6">What you'll walk away with</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li class="text-foreground/80"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Clarity on where AI fits in your specific workflow</li>
        <li class="text-foreground/80"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Hands-on experience with your highest-yield AI use case</li>
        <li class="text-foreground/80"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Repetitive work identified and matched with tailored AI solutions</li>
        <li class="text-foreground/80"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Security and data privacy assessment for your context</li>
        <li class="text-foreground/80"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>A concrete plan for practically incorporating AI into your daily workflow</li>
        <li class="text-foreground/80"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>A signed diploma certifying completed AI upskilling</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Real results -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground/50 font-medium mb-6">Results from previous sessions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-accent/7 rounded-lg border border-accent/10">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground/90 mb-3">Environmental Consultant — Water Ecology</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
            <li class="text-foreground/70"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Report drafting cut by 50–70% per document</li>
            <li class="text-foreground/70"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Voice memos from site visits turned into structured drafts automatically</li>
            <li class="text-foreground/70"><span class="text-foreground/30 mr-2">-</span>Proofreading and quality review 70–90% faster</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent font-medium">15–25 hours/week in potential time savings</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing + Purchase -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground/50 font-medium mb-6">Book your session</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-2">
        <span class="font-medium text-foreground/90">9,900 SEK per session (excl. VAT).</span> Pre-interview questionnaire, session, and report included.
      </p>
      <BookingForm appsScriptUrl={appsScriptUrl} />
    </section>

    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      <Image
        src={avatarImage}
        alt="Daniel Grahn"
        class="rounded-full border border-foreground/10 size-20 aspect-square"
        width={160}
        height={160}
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Why -->
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground/50 font-medium mb-6">Why I'm uniquely positioned to help you</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
        The recent breakthroughs in AI are going to transform most knowledge work — not in some distant future, but right now. I've seen firsthand how much time and energy people can reclaim once AI is properly integrated into their workflow. I want to help speed that up. The sooner people build real competence with these tools, the sooner they benefit — and that's what drives me to do this work.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mt-3">
        My background in software engineering, AI development, product ownership, UX, and stakeholder management means I don't just understand the technology — I understand how it needs to fit into real teams, real processes, and real business constraints. That combination is what makes this coaching practical, not theoretical.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
